window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Number-one <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Vince Flynn - “the best pure adrenaline-charged action writer out there today” (<i>The Providence Journal</i>) - puts Mitch Rapp in the crossfire as America’s enemies tighten their grip. </p> <p>Returning from a covert mission, Mitch Rapp was publicly hailed by the president for his role in the fight against terrorism. After years of working in the shadows, Rapp was caught in the media spotlight - and marked for death by virtually every terrorist in the world. Now a CIA advisor, Rapp is ready to battle terror far from the front lines. </p> <p>But when a Navy SEAL team in the Philippines is ambushed, all evidence points to a leak within the U.S. State Department. And a greater threat lurks - a ruthless assassin working for the most powerful men in the Middle East, who are bent on igniting a world war. With the world watching, Rapp must hold back the flames of Armageddon....</p>"; 
